settings.description: Cannons to the LEFT of me.. BOOTS! BOOTS! Bullets to the RIGHT o' me.. BOMBS! BOMBS! I'm going mad.. it's the desert madness! AAAAA! -- at the end of room 2, the warp exit is under the centre block.
A long and vegetable filled adventure. A mini Mario game I guess?
From boomerang pirouettes to rolling balls of pain .. just jump into the purely psychotic sand -- enemies and all. Made in August of '21 .. updated improvements over the last week.
When were there so many pipes in the sky? Who knows, but for whatever reason Mario needs to get through all the piranhas and koopas.
Things get mysterious at night. Use pullied platforms and pipes to traverse piranhas and hot heads.

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.

This level has 5 ace coins, so you need to recollect it,
Infact, this is my nice level ever made, you need a hammer to destroy it by getting the 3-ups in a giant question mark block.
I am making a wood floor for now, this adventure is way easy so find the hidden ace coins
You have 200 seconds to pass this level
This is the first level in Super Mario World
This is the desert of pyramid, well the desert here looks like hot and well want an underground base to explore the cave.
A venture to stop the Koopalings, travelling from Airship to Tanks.
Iggy's refined airship, most likely to stop Mario but maybe he just wanted a new fancier airship eh?
Pick up coins from the ground, and go underground and collect them there
I might make a part 2 for more areas
Hammers are practically everywhere, attacking from all sides! Make sure to avoid them!

Solve difficult puzzles while keeping Mario on his toes in this icy but warm ghost house.   

To carry Flurries, check out the Flurry Carrying level. You'll solve the first puzzle much quicker.
Smaghetti is really not functioning properly, everything was working fine one day, and then the other it starts glitching out. Just ignore the graphical issues. I hope this gets patched.
